    "text": "IN THE FEDERAL COURT OF AUSTRALIA QUEENSLAND DISTRICT REGISTRY GENERAL DIVISION No. QG 171 of 1992 BETWEEN: DAVIDS HOLDINGS PROPRIETARY LIMITED Appellant AND: COLES MYER LIMITED Respondent EX TEMPORE REASONS FOR JUDGMENT CORAM: — BLACK CJ, RYAN, HILL JJ PLACE: BRISBANE DATE: 20 NOVEMBER 1992 THE COURT: This is an application by Davids Holdings oe Limited for leave to appeal from a judgment of a judge of this court declining further to extend an interim injunction restraining the first respondent, Coles Myer Limited, from acquiring or taking any step to acquire any shares in QIW Retailers Limited (QIW).",
