    "original_source_path": "newapp/dataset=decision/decision/commonwealth/1992/decision_commonwealth_1992_caf4830a.json",
    "text": "We have referred to the applications to extend the interim injunction. It should be noted, however, that the extension of the interim injunction was sought in the course of an application for interlocutory relief, which is still continuing, in which further evidence may yet be adduced and in respect of which a notice to Coles Myer to produce documents is proposed to be called on.",
